      <t>This draft proposes Fast Route Attestation (FRA), an efficient mechanism for securing AS paths and preventing prefix hijacking by signing critical AS path segments (i.e., adjacent AS triples). FRA can achieve similar level of security as S-BGP/BGPSec, but with much higher efficiency.</t>
